Radware Defense Pro

In order to feed this application, you have to configure DefensePro to send syslog messages to your Splunk instances.

Go to your Vision console, and select your DefensePro.
Then go to "Configuration -> Setup -> Reporting Settings -> Syslog"

Click on "+" and add your Splunk listener with its IP and listening port.

The sourcetype of your logs must be set to DefensePro in Splunk
